      "column": "left",
      "text": "Zitrejus un Remmeschus/ ka ta KUNGA Nams atjaunahts tap-tu/ ir tahdus/ kas fapratte Dsel-fi un Warru kalt/ ka ta KUN-GA Nams atkat taptu stipri-nahts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta darrija tee Wehrmin-deri/ ka tas Darbs zaur winav Rohkn atkat par labbu ktua/ un tee istatsija to Deewa Namnu atkat pareist/ un stiprinaja to.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Rad tee to nu bij pabeigufchi/ tad atneffe tee to atlif-kutchu Naudu pee to Kehninu un Jojadu/ un tas likke Rihkus darriht preekch ta KUNGA Namma/ Darba Rihkus/ ir par teem Dedfamo- Uppuxeem/ un Karvotes/selta un tudraba Trau-kus/ tee uppureja weenumehr Dedfamo-Uppuxus ta KUNGA Namnâ/ famehr Jojadus dsih-woja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Jojadus tappe wezz un labbi peedsihwojis/ un nomir-re/ wiꞥſch bija fimts un trihs-definits Gaddus wezz/ kad tas nomirre.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee aprakfe to Dahwi-da Villi pee teem Kehnixeem/ jo wiꞥſch bij Israëtam labbi dar-rijs/ tik labbi pee Deewa ka pee winan Namma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet kad Jojadus bija no-miris/ tad nahze tee Leeli-Kun-gi no Juhda/ un paƙlannijahs preekch to Kehninu/ tad paƙlaut-fija teem tas Kehnisch.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee pamette ta KUN-GA farvu Tehwu Deewa Nam-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "mu/ un falpoja teem Elka Dscheem un Elkeem/ tad nu Dufniba pahr Juhdu un Je-salemi/ schahs winnu leelas seegschanas deht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tatschu wiꞥſch pee te fuhtija Praweeschus/ ka kee tee pee ta KUNGA atkat atgreeft tee gann dewe Leezibu prett wneein/ bet tee tahs Aufis ne greese.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ta KUNGA G apgehrbe Zakariju/ ta Preeka Jojadus Dehlu/ tas uskalahda augsta Weetâ/ fur tee Gadis bija/ un fazzija us teem: Sjakka Deews/kapehz pahrkahpiuhs ta KUNGA Bauslus/ eijums par labbu ne buhs? ju-effat to KUNGU atstahjustad wiꞥſch juhs arridsan atstal\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee darrija weenu Diribu prett winnu/ un noimehja to ar Akminieem pehz ta Kinina Pawehlefchanas/ eeekshKUNGA Namna Pagalmja\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta ne peeminneja t Kehnisch Joas tahs Schehlasbas/ ko fchi pascha Tehws Jadus tam bij parahdijs/ bet nekawe winna Dehla. Un kad tonomirre/ fazzija wiꞥſch: TKUNG'S to redsehs un mekfle\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad nu tas GaddRahrts bija pagahjis/ tad ze-lahs prett winnu to SihreKarra-Spehks/ un tee mahprett Juhdu un Jerusalemt/ u-nomaitaja no teem Laudim wis fus Lanschu Wirfneekus/ un fu\n"
    }
